body:
It&#039;s not a big deal, and I wasn&#039;t gonna post about it cuz I&#039;ve never posted before and it was low-key intimidating, but this seems fine and I finally got mad enough at it to post about it.
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}} 
For a while now, like a few patches ago, Ekko&#039;s homeguard animation hasn&#039;t ended after his movement speed gets low enough; he just kinda keeps taking these huge, super slow strides around until you stop moving, then he finally starts walking normally again. Again, it&#039;s not a big deal, by no means is it something that needs to be rushed ASAP, but I hope it&#039;s on the list of things that need fixing.

replies.body:
